{"tid":1486332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府:Noted with thanks","createTime":"2019-08-19T00:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T00:34:24.000Z","uid":284295,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be42903ebe0f9ee3b6f180503c3b6a9c07fd3716","tid":1486332,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:07:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/18/P2019081800818.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F18%2FP2019081800818.htm&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=32a24b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/18/P2019081800818.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府就維園集會作出回應<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　政府發言人今日（八月十八日）回應在維多利亞公園舉辦的公眾集會時表示，雖然集會期間大致和平，但由於參與者佔用了港島多條主要幹道，路面交通大受影響，對市民造成不便。運輸署與警方已積極協調，盡量將影響減至最少。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　發言人重申，目前最重要的是要盡快回復社會秩序；當一切平靜之後，政府會與市民展開真誠對話，致力修補撕裂，重建社會和諧。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月18日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時18分<br />\n<br />\n準備升級啦咁多位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05352543430632d31578f8539334140bb61705e0","tid":1486332,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:09:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80f8fb2e85ed4b2dd0723c5c34e27684eeec5296","tid":1486332,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"當一切平靜之後，政府會與市民展開真誠對話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123213b768092488438ea09d4b9d2495a5183134","tid":1486332,"uid":22822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:22:12.000Z","msg":"佢真係以為我地同佢地一樣ON9，完咗食屎都得<br />\n<br />\n我認為係因為我哋示威者地嘅解說唔夠，日後會加強宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbfc5bbeffe145982feaf387586fecf1a4b9aab","tid":1486332,"uid":292362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:22:59.000Z","msg":"真係有thanks....?!"},{"pid":"dc927e16b868eb08c39f11c23345a1e6557573c9","tid":1486332,"uid":153254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:23:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2649039151796885&amp;id=223783954322429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2649039151796885%26id%3D223783954322429&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=c2f78b11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2649039151796885&amp;id=223783954322429</a>"},{"pid":"66c42f7c34c169adcf6c443fc5247a6d5cdb52f2","tid":1486332,"uid":153254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:23:52.000Z","msg":"通識教育純邏輯討論：試論虛偽之極致<br />\n<br />\n「政府發言人重申，目前最重要的是要盡快回復社會秩序；當一切平靜之後，政府會與市民展開真誠對話，致力修補撕裂，重建社會和諧。」<br />\n<br />\n如此看來；<br />\n<br />\n1. 「真誠對話」的前設是「一切平靜」。<br />\n2. 即如果市民平靜了，政府就展開「真誠對話」。<br />\n3. 但如果政府提出的對話不合市民心意，或未能滿足社會訴求，社會難免又開始「不平靜了」。<br />\n4. 由於「真誠對話」的前設是「一切平靜」，所以當社會又因政府沒有回應訴求而「不平靜」時，原來「真誠對話」又要被迫結束了。<br />\n5. 所以「真誠對話」其實就是社會要全盤接受政府的看法，因為只要有異見，就是「不平靜」，沒有「社會和諧」。<br />\n6. 所以「真誠對話」的前設，就是市民要先在沒有前設下全盤接受政府的看法。<br />\n7. 直到2047，也不會有「真誠對話」。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n(Source: avenger@我們一個秘密離地群組，感謝其他朋友改良分享）"},{"pid":"2822d1035f2de5bf5c4dcf46a773323f312eebe2","tid":1486332,"uid":307857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:24:17.000Z","msg":"重係度擺官威"},{"pid":"68b4bcd8d976fe84208079b89cb0f2d3ae0c3584","tid":1486332,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"真係當你死㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a912a841d47c0e3e754231e4bffd29b8c01fd1","tid":1486332,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:25:22.000Z","msg":"頂盡只係noted, 無thanks"},{"pid":"7be18afb6dad527b4df82320d602f513a78ce9f0","tid":1486332,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:25:25.000Z","msg":"尋日咁撚和平，你幾時有真誠既回應呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾幾日時間你囉，無反應我地就做野架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbdf195bb55c8c55d1cf4389636377da5cbe408","tid":1486332,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:27:38.000Z","msg":"和理非遊行唔係期望政府會立即回應<br />\n而係比大家見到仲有好多人支持我地爭取既野<br />\n同埋政府一次又一次漠視民意<br />\n<br />\n老實講而家不論係勇武定和理非活動都係迫唔到政府回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n惟有持續升級同聯合其他國家既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d105176e091d4e07f43daf55d6a6c439f75a010","tid":1486332,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:33:29.000Z","msg":"攞正牌勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ff5596bf1c8f1bdc1d980318bf1c266ccf91c1","tid":1486332,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:34:24.000Z","msg":"呢個時間仲咁口硬<br />\n真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}